ZH: 我们计划走访这个地区的居民来了解他们的需求。
EN: We plan to visit the residents of this area to understand their needs.

ZH: 他们打算走访所有的客户以确认他们的满意度。
EN: They intend to visit all customers to confirm their satisfaction.

ZH: 我们会定期走访各个部门，了解他们的工作情况。
EN: We will regularly visit each department to understand their work situations.

ZH: 请你走访一下这个地方，看看安全问题。
EN: Could you visit this place and check for safety issues?

ZH: 我们需要走访几家潜在的供应商，以选出最合适的合作伙伴。
EN: We need to visit several potential suppliers to choose the most suitable partner.

ZH: 近期我们将走访一些老客户，了解他们的反馈意见。
EN: In the near future, we will visit some old clients to gather their feedback.

ZH: 希望你能走访一下这个项目地点，看看有没有什么需要改进的地方。
EN: I hope you can visit the project site and see if there are any areas that need improvement.

ZH: 明天我们要走访这个新市场，看看有没有机会发展业务。
EN: Tomorrow we will visit this new market to see if there are any opportunities for business development.

ZH: 我们需要走访一些行业领军企业，学习他们的最佳实践。
EN: We need to visit some industry-leading companies to learn from their best practices.

ZH: 负责人已经走访了几家潜在的投资者，希望能够得到资金支持。
EN: The manager has visited several potential investors in the hopes of securing financial support.

ZH: 请务必走访一下我们的供应链，确保生产不会出现问题。
EN: Please make sure to visit our supply chain to ensure smooth production.

ZH: 在考察过程中，我们会走访一些当地企业，了解他们的经营情况。
EN: During the inspection process, we will visit some local companies to understand their business operations.

ZH: 她专门走访了几个乡村偏远地区，为当地居民提供医疗服务。
EN: She specifically visited several remote rural areas to provide medical services to the local residents.

ZH: 这次调查需要走访一些重要的业界人士，以获取更多信息。
EN: This survey requires visiting some important industry figures to gather more information.

ZH: 我们已经走访了五家竞争对手，了解他们的市场定位。
EN: We have visited five competitors to understand their market positioning.

