EN: Tomorrow we will visit several potential partners to discuss future cooperation plans.

ZH: 他们走访了几家外国公司，希望能够找到合作机会。
EN: They visited several foreign companies in the hopes of finding collaboration opportunities.

ZH: 我们必须走访一下客户，了解他们对我们产品的需求。
EN: We must visit customers to understand their needs for our products.

